description_expanded: Fujifilm Instax Mini Instant Film Twin Pack (20 Sheets) is designed to deliver everyday reliability with thoughtful details suited for electronics. Twin pack of Fujifilm Instax Mini instant film, yielding 20 credit-card-sized prints. White border frame. Compatible with all Instax Mini cameras. Built for convenience and value, it balances quality materials with practical features you can rely on at home, on the go, or as a thoughtful gift.
